Luis Herrera de la Fuente (April 25, 1916 – December 5, 2014) was a Mexican conductor, pianist, violinist, composer and writer of the 20th century.
He conducted the Orquesta Sinfónica Nacional of Mexico for 18 years.
He died on December 5, 2014 at the age of 98.
